---
title: "Join Us - Designer - Join our team as a designer"

header:
  title: "join us"
  subtitle: "strategic designer"

introduction:
  title: "At Unboxed, design is a team sport"
  text_1: "We have a brilliant team of agile folk with an impressive reputation for creating great digital services in both the public and private sector."
  text_2: "We are looking for a talented and confident strategic designer to join us."

design_image:
  image: "/jobs/images/designer.jpg"
  image_description: "Designer at work"

description:
  title: "We need someone who"
  requirements:
    - Has a breadth of experience several different design disciplines
    - Is a strategic thinker, comfortable with uncertainty and complexity
    - Takes a highly collaborative approach, facilitating design within teams
    - Is a passionate advocate for Design Thinking and Lean and Agile principles
    - Loves to get out and learn from users, customers and stakeholders

design_quote:
  quote: "For me, design is as much about attitude as it is about experience or specific expertise. Great looking visuals and considered user journeys are important but I most enjoy working with designers who are open in their thinking and encourage the team to collectively tackle and solve important problems."
  source: "Martyn Evans, Head of Product"
  image: "/assets/images/people/martyn-evans.png"

contact_us:
  title: "Send us your CV"
  text_1: "Claire is our “people gardener” and she would love to hear from you."
  text_2: "We like to do the most valuable things first - employing you could be exactly that."
  text_3: "Send your CV through to Claire at: "
  email: "iwantajob@unboxed.co"
  text_4: "From there, she'll be in touch. Good luck!"
  image: "/jobs/images/ubxd-gardener-2.jpg"
  image_description: "Our gardener"

related:
  title: "Related"
  articles:
    - title: "The five day design sprint with Guy’s & St. Thomas’ NHS Foundation Trust Paediatric Allergy Team"
      type: "blog"
      link: "/blog/the-five-day-design-sprint-with-guy-s-st-thomas-nhs-foundation-trust-pediatric-allergy-team"

    - title: "Welcome to the team: Boris Divjak"
      type: "blog"
      link: "/blog/welcome-to-the-team-boris-divjak"

    - title: "Shaking up early product development, part 1: Using journey mapping to improve your user journey"
      type: "blog"
      link: "/blog/shaking-up-early-product-development-part-1-using-journey-mapping-to-improve-your-user-journey"
---

<header class="page-header page-header--bottom-margin">
  <div class="job-page-header__container">
    <h1 class="job-page-header__introduction">
      <a href="/jobs"><%= current_page.data.header.title %></a>
      <span> / <%= current_page.data.header.subtitle %></span>
    </h1>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container" data-header-waypoint>
  <section class="component">
    <div class="text-tile--full-width">
      <h2 class="text-tile__title">
        <%= current_page.data.introduction.title %>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-tile__paragraph--with-spacing">
        <%= current_page.data.introduction.text_1 %>
      </p>
      <p class="text-tile__paragraph--with-spacing">
        <%= current_page.data.introduction.text_2 %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%= image_tag current_page.data.design_image.image, alt: current_page.data.design_image.image_description, class: "full-image", srcset: retina_srcset(current_page.data.design_image.image) %>

  <section class="component">
    <div class="text-tile--full-width">
      <h2 class="text-tile__title">
        <%= current_page.data.description.title %>
      </h2>

      <ul class="text-tile__list">
        <% current_page.data.description.requirements.each do |requirement| %>
          <li class="text-tile__list-item">
            <%= requirement %>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <blockquote class="quote">
    <aside class="quote__right-section">
      <p class="quote__text--centered">
        <%= current_page.data.design_quote.quote %>
      </p>
      <p class="quote__source">
        <%= current_page.data.design_quote.source %>
      </p>
    </aside>
    <img class="quote__source-image" src="<%= current_page.data.design_quote.image %>" alt="<%= current_page.data.design_quote.source %>"/>
  </blockquote>

  <section class="component">
    <div class="component__tile text-tile">
      <h2 class="text-tile__title--lowercase">
        <%= current_page.data.contact_us.title %>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-tile__paragraph--with-spacing">
        <%= current_page.data.contact_us.text_1 %>
      </p>

      <p class="text-tile__paragraph--with-spacing">
        <a href="mailto:<%= current_page.data.contact_us.email %>"><%= current_page.data.contact_us.email %></a>
      </p>

      <p class="text-tile__paragraph--with-spacing">
        <%= current_page.data.contact_us.text_2 %>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="component__tile image-tile">
      <%= image_tag current_page.data.contact_us.image, alt: current_page.data.contact_us.image_description, class: "image-tile__image", srcset: retina_srcset(current_page.data.contact_us.image) %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%= partial 'project-stories/related_tiles' %>
</div>
